7.	Look into pillage formula.  Make taxing a bit more attractive.

8.	Consider alternate DWIM approaches for order execution.

	Estimate time order will take, allow stack members to finish
	zero-time orders before beginning time-taking orders.


9.	Make travel times longer.

		No route should be less than 10 days (?)
		Lengthen sea routes
		Perhaps horses give a 25% bonus?

